      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>creamy smoked basa parcels </strong>with the <strong>parsley mash</strong>, <strong>glazed carrots </strong>and <strong>cranberry sauce</strong> to the side</p><p>Sprinkle the <strong>remaining chopped parsley </strong>over the mash</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
